    <p>We use cookies to enhance your browsing experience.</p>
    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions or concerns, please contact us at <a href="mailto:info@contosopizza.com">info@contosopizza.com</a>.</p>
</body>
</html>
